{"tid":249391,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【4月新番】 劍姬神聖譚 06","createTime":"2017-05-19T09:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T15:59:45.000Z","uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"448c1a61742de64e6961b56a2d6bf0a32469f442","tid":249391,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T09:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fGRSpYr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfGRSpYr.jpg&h=d01488a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正傳只有149句台詞的【劍姬】艾絲&middot;華倫斯坦。<br />\n以最強聞名的女劍士今天也和同伴們一起，<br />\n前往廣大的地下迷宮「地下城」。<br />\n腐朽成灰的龍的殘骸，隱藏於暗處的異常事態<br />\n在種種神秘的威脅來襲的深層域50階層，<br />\n艾絲呼喚疾風，在迷宮的黑暗中刻下一閃！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;之後來訪的是，與少年的「邂逅」<br />\n「那個&hellip;&hellip;你，沒事嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n在迷宮都市歐拉麗之地，<br />\n少女與少年的物語鮮烈地交錯！<br />\n<br />\n這是，另一個眷族的物語，<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;【劍姬神聖譚Sword Oratoria】&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\nSTAFF<br />\n原作：大森藤ノ<br />\n角色原案：灰村清孝、安田典生<br />\n監督：鈴木洋平<br />\n系列構成：白根秀樹<br />\n角色設計：木本茂樹<br />\n音樂：井內啟二<br />\n動畫製作：J.C.STAFF<br />\n<br />\nCAST<br />\n艾絲&middot;華倫斯坦:大西沙織<br />\n蕾菲亞&middot;維里迪斯:木村珠莉<br />\n蒂奧娜&middot;席呂特:村川梨衣<br />\n蒂奧涅&middot;席呂特:高橋未奈美<br />\n洛基:久保由利香<br />\n芬恩&middot;蒂姆那:田村睦心<br />\n里維莉雅&middot;利歐斯&middot;阿爾弗:川澄綾子(正傳動畫版:種田梨沙)<br />\n貝爾&middot;克朗尼：松岡禎丞<br />\n赫斯緹雅：水瀨祈<br />\nviu逢星期五深夜 03:30更新<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ:外傳跟正傳有何關連<br />\nA:外傳是以【劍姬】和洛基眷族作為主視點的故事,而時間點和正傳是一樣的<br />\nQ:正傳主角會否出場<br />\nA:由於跟正傳是同一時間點,所以同樣會有艾絲和貝爾相會的情節[/quote]op:RE-ILLUSION<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LxCMaZUzhVc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLxCMaZUzhVc&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=5ba4e2f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LxCMaZUzhVc</a><br />\n 第6話 WEB予告<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/xUA7b0PQ6ojejG13UI/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FxUA7b0PQ6ojejG13UI%2Fgiphy.gif&h=2f2d7dbc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a266f44f5b637819523c8b04f9646a9db15a167","tid":249391,"uid":99827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T09:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78e5583b55a9892e4458ebaa063981ab9cc84bc4","tid":249391,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T09:25:08.000Z","msg":"報到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/19/172507_42d8e4a1b3ff62b14b9bcec8de6c4877.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F19%2F172507_42d8e4a1b3ff62b14b9bcec8de6c4877.jpg&h=047cd45f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbd382edc136faba72806b79f9a543646204f159","tid":249391,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T11:45:25.000Z","msg":"半集打樓層主，半集艾絲賣萌"},{"pid":"ec2a48621853bb2ca1e116e9047903b36367e1f3","tid":249391,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T15:43:27.000Z","msg":"隻樓層主弱化到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc398892ef6fb9357a43b480ec262a50790db8b","tid":249391,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T15:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/19/234511_99412becca860bdb4223db744a94003c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F19%2F234511_99412becca860bdb4223db744a94003c.jpg&h=841a6cde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3451e8209b5c9f436e3a5423791e2476894049e0","tid":249391,"uid":99827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T15:49:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻樓層主弱化到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/